description: Big Suzie's Little Bakery is here with the sweetest treats to ever hit the Buffalo streets! Down home desserts that taste just like they came straight from grandma's oven are right around the corner with this mobile bakery. Whether you're looking to satisfy your sweet tooth on the move or need an awesome dessert for your next special occasion, Big Suzie's Little Bakery is perfect for you!
name: Big Suzie’s Little Bakery
